ONLY Good VIBES AND MONEY ARMY JACKET

NO ROOM FOR ANYTHING ELSE!

DETAILS:

Designed and printed in the USA, sweatshop-free.

DTG, Screen or Vinyl Print.

Unisex fit.

Photo is for design display only. The actual cut of the jacket may vary.

Unisex Size Instructions:

Our unisex tees are sold in standard men's sizes. Women will typically need to order one size down in these tees. Please see the examples below:

Unisex to Women's Conversion

Unisex XSmall = Women's S

Unisex Small = Women's M

Unisex Medium = Women's L

Unisex Large = Women's XL

Unisex XLarge = Women's 2X

Unisex 2X Large = Women's 3X
